app_details.title: My M-Pesa
app_details.description: Welcome to the new M-Pesa App! M-Pesa, the most innovative financial services app in Mozambique, enhances your experience by launching version 2.17.2 of the M-Pesa App. Enjoy amazing user experience on our revamped M-Pesa app, built with you in mind. With the Vodacom mini app, you can now enjoy well curated GSM offerings on the M-Pesa super app. Your referral bonuses will now be credited to your M-Pesa account instantly, with the Automatic Cashback capability implemented with this version. Download the latest M-Pesa app and enjoy this new experience!
app_details.descriptionHTML:
Welcome to the new M-Pesa App!

M-Pesa, the most innovative financial services app in Mozambique, enhances your experience by launching version 2.17.2 of the M-Pesa App.

Enjoy amazing user experience on our revamped M-Pesa app, built with you in mind. With the Vodacom mini app, you can now enjoy well curated GSM offerings on the M-Pesa super app. Your referral bonuses will now be credited to your M-Pesa account instantly, with the Automatic Cashback capability implemented with this version.

Download the latest M-Pesa app and enjoy this new experience!
app_details.summary: M-Pesa is the fastest and safest way to transact digitally in Mozambique.

content.61: App razoável, mas com muitos pontos negativos: -Sempre que mudas de telefone, tens que fazer um novo setup, o que é desperdício de tempo. Neste aspecto, fica a perder para o *150#. Bastava usar só uma password e/ou OTP. -Transações com valores limite muito baixos. No máximo só recebe 25,000 MT (cerca de 300 USD) doutras plataformas, o que é muito pouco, já que nem chega para pagar conta de luz, água, renda, empregada, muito pouco. -E outras complicações já mencionadas por outros utilizadores.
